MMB: MMBench [32]; MME [14] and MME-P: MME-Perception. We include approaches with continuous visual inputs (top) versus discrete visual inputs (bottom). The best results among approaches with discrete visual input are highlighted in bold. * results are not reported in original paper and tested with lmms-eval [71] using the released checkpoint. When calculating average, we use MME-P and divide it by 20 to have the same scale with other benchmarks.
